        "id": "ex07-tab",
        "type": "tab",
        "label": "07 - Call a Method",
        "info": "Call an OPC UA method. The Object and Method NodeIds are configured in the node. Input arguments are passed via msg.payload as an array of {dataType, value}.\n\nThis example uses the included Docker test server. Start it with:\n\n    docker compose up -d\n\nThe test server provides:\n  - ns=1;s=Methods.Add (A:Double, B:Double) → Result:Double\n  - ns=1;s=Methods.Multiply (A:Double, B:Double) → Result:Double\n\nResult is in msg.payload (array of output values)."
    },
    {
        "id": "ex07-comment",
        "type": "comment",
        "z": "ex07-tab",
        "name": "Add(2, 3) and Multiply(4, 5) on the included test server",
